=== Division By Zero Test ===
100 / 10 = 10
100 / 5 = 20
Warning: Division by zero, returning 0
100 / 0 = 0
100 / 2 = 50
1000 / 20 = 50
Caught: Division by zero error
1000 / 0 = -1
1000 / 25 = 40
100 % 7 = 2
100 % 0 = -1
100 % 3 = 1
Complex(5): 100
Complex(2): 100
Complex(0): 0
Complex(10): 50
Division by zero complete
